[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0004","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0004.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0140","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 RAS/PPTP 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 3.51 及 NT 4.0 的远程访问服务（RAS）与 PPTP 协议实现中存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证，通过向目标系统发送特制的畸形控制数据包，可导致 RAS/PPTP 服务崩溃或停止响应，造成系统无法正常提供远程访问功能。该漏洞无需用户交互即可远程触发，影响范围涉及企业远程接入环境，可能导致业务中断。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0140"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-06-30T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:40.957","remediation":"安装 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 4 或更高版本以修复 RAS/PPTP 协议处理中的缺陷。由于 Windows NT 4.0 已停止支持，建议升级至受支持的 Windows Server 版本（如 Windows Server 2019/2022），并在防火墙上限制对 PPTP 端口（TCP 1723）的访问以降低暴露风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0140","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20508","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0140.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0140","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0140.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0140.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0140.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-fg49-hp4g-2h7r/GHSA-fg49-hp4g-2h7r.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/W/winnt_pptp_dos.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0140.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0004.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0715","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0715.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0916","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9103,\"outputTokens\":18,\"totalTokens\":10785}}","description":"标签之间。<value>WebTrends软件存在权限许可漏洞，将账户名和密码存储在访问权限未受限制的文件中。攻击者若具备对目标系统的本地或网络访问权限，可直接读取该文件获取敏感凭据，进而实现对系统的未授权访问。该漏洞影响运行WebTrends软件的服务器平台，可能导致敏感信息泄露，CVSS评分2.1。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0916"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-06-29T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:19.420","remediation":"升级 WebTrends 软件至官方已修复该漏洞的最新版本。将存储账户名和密码的文件访问权限修改为仅管理员可读写（如 Windows 系统设置为仅 SYSTEM 账户和 Administrators 组拥有完全控制权限，其他用户拒绝所有访问）。如暂时无法升级，可将敏感配置文件迁移至受保护目录并设置严格 ACL 访问控制，同时定期审计文件权限设置。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0916","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/a3f034241443c2295538d03be5945be20fc1cca3/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0916.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0916","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0916.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a6294b4e43a4333eb79c2542461b42377b040bdc/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0916.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/ea59c529438222532763b90ba7dc8295b318be99/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6x5p-9rf7-4rx3/GHSA-6x5p-9rf7-4rx3.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0916.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000683.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0916.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0715.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1081","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1081.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1365","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统在查找关键系统程序（如 NDDEAGNT.EXE、EXPLORER.EXE、USERINIT.EXE 或 TASKMGR.EXE）时，默认优先搜索 %systemroot% 用户主目录而非系统目录。由于该目录默认可写，本地攻击者可将木马程序放入其中，系统启动或调用时优先执行恶意程序，从而绕过访问限制或提升权限。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 系列系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1365"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-28T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:17.093","remediation":"限制 %systemroot% 目录的写入权限，仅允许 Administrators 和 SYSTEM 账户写入；修改系统路径搜索顺序，确保系统目录（%systemroot%\\system32）优先于用户目录被搜索；建议升级至 Windows 2000 或更高版本，该版本已修复此路径搜索顺序问题。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=93069418400856&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=93127894731200&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/515","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2336","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1365.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1365","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1365.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1365.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-xwwx-gqwv-7rqx/GHSA-xwwx-gqwv-7rqx.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1365.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--f9a5326b-c12e-4178-a970-49378c5906df.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idbypass","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_gainpre.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/4a6e09a063689f2d97734100478c1eef6f6dc387/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1081.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0735","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0735.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0938","title":"MBone SDR 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"MBone SDR 软件包在处理 Session Initiation Protocol (SIP) 消息时未对用户输入的特殊字符进行有效过滤，导致远程攻击者可通过在 SIP 消息中注入 shell 元字符（如管道符、分号等）触发命令注入漏洞，从而在目标系统上以 SDR 进程权限执行任意命令。该漏洞影响早期 MBone 多播骨干网环境中的 SDR 会话目录工具，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0938"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-06-28T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:22.043","remediation":"立即卸载 MBone SDR Package 软件，该软件已停止维护且不再有安全更新。改用现代会话目录工具（如基于 Web 的会议调度系统）替代。如暂时无法卸载，在防火墙层面过滤 UDP/TCP 端口 4444（SDR 默认端口）及 SIP 相关流量，并限制仅允许可信 IP 访问 SDR 服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0938","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/aa3114da1227373bef7855dba21bcaa5f0e0ad76/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0938.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0938","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-0938.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/b4ddb28f94d250449ab64c1617f45b1f91701fa2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0938.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/bf2339193e1c10dc2db330718adeb8cc8d88c4dd/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-462x-8j67-jx8m/GHSA-462x-8j67-jx8m.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0938.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000680.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0938.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0735.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0346","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0346.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0733","title":"VMware 1.0.1 Linux 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"VMware Workstation 1.0.1 for Linux 版本中存在本地缓冲区溢出漏洞。由于 VMware 二进制程序以 setuid root 权限安装且未对 HOME 环境变量长度做充分边界检查，本地攻击者可通过设置超长的 HOME 环境变量触发栈缓冲区溢出，覆盖函数返回地址并执行任意代码，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞攻击复杂度低，无需特殊权限，CVSS v2 评分 7.2，危害等级高。已有公开的漏洞利用代码（EDB-19371）可实现完全控制目标系统。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0733"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-06-26T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:56.623","remediation":"立即升级 VMware 至最新版本（VMware Workstation Pro 17.x 或 VMware Player 17.x），旧版本 VMware 1.0.1 已停止支持且存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。若暂时无法升级，应限制 HOME 环境变量长度不超过 4096 字节，并通过文件系统权限（chmod 700）限制 VMware 二进制文件仅允许授权用户执行。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/490","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19371","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0f25967d744704fe14324ac10f2b57e945aed081/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0733.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0733","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0733.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/82035e540ee415f78310ba979a19dffd78d3cfa2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0733.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8b1565557a8e0fb04634f0989d7e7dd7febd4847/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-gw48-hr89-vwq9/GHSA-gw48-hr89-vwq9.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0733.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0346.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0992","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0992.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1164","title":"Microsoft Outlook 97/98/2000 X-UIDL Header 远程拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Outlook 97/98/2000 在处理电子邮件 X-UIDL 头字段时存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者通过向目标用户发送多条包含相同 X-UIDL 标头的恶意邮件，可导致 Outlook 客户端在处理邮件时发生挂起甚至崩溃。攻击无需用户交互，仅需打开收件箱即可触发。该漏洞影响 Outlook 97/98/2000 版本，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1164"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-06-25T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:51.417","remediation":"该漏洞影响已停止支持的 Outlook 97/98/2000，微软未发布官方补丁。建议升级到 Outlook 2003 或更高版本（如 Office 365），新版本已修复此问题。如无法升级，可在邮件服务器或客户端侧配置规则过滤含重复 X-UIDL 头的邮件作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93041631215856&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1164.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1164","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1164.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d0a8c476da89b37a2bbb6193b7964b10d03aff75/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1164.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-f498-r72q-hr69/GHSA-f498-r72q-hr69.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1164.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--1c5b691b-669f-4f27-ad1d-2fbaec345e2b.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/be7ad03fdf3a412f0fd57a25f1732dc0ecfb1cb3/1999.tsv","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dos.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0992.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0512","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0512.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0778","title":"Xi Graphics Accelerated-X 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Xi Graphics Accelerated-X 服务器版本 4.0.x 和 5.0 存在本地缓冲区溢出漏洞。该漏洞源于程序对 display 或 query 参数缺乏长度校验，本地攻击者可通过传递超长参数触发栈溢出，覆盖返回地址实现任意代码执行，从而获取 root 权限。影响版本包括 Accelerated-X 4.0.x 至 5.0 系列，CVSS 评分 7.2，属高危漏洞。攻击需具备本地登录权限，利用方式为构造恶意长参数调用易受攻击的 X 服务组件。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0778"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"1999-06-25","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 Xi Graphics Accelerated-X 至 5.0 以上安全版本；若无官方补丁，可移除 Xaccel 二进制文件的 setuid root 权限（chmod u-s /usr/X11R6/bin/Xaccel），限制本地非授权用户执行该程序，并禁用 -query 和 -display 参数传递超长输入","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/488","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19370","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/abfccbe3a11aa2b9dde2cfba5a12ba6256820a51/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0778.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0778","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0778.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/ed6bb242e8dd7e27b54cbf189349b0ad2ae7c304/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0778.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/780ea229276a503f17a45c7ccc9fc5e26e6b2447/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5qr3-wfmq-mc4w/GHSA-5qr3-wfmq-mc4w.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0778.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_3.list.dict","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000678.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19370"],"exp_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19370"],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0512.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1121","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1121.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1470","title":"Eastman Work Management 密码明文存储漏洞","description":"Eastman Work Management 3.21 存在密码明文存储漏洞，该软件将用户密码以明文形式保存在 Windows 注册表的 COMMON 和 LOCATOR 键值中。本地攻击者可通过读取注册表获取明文密码，进而提升权限。该漏洞影响 Eastman Work Management 3.21 版本，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。建议升级至修复版本或限制注册表访问权限。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1470"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-24T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:30.620","remediation":"立即限制对注册表项 COMMON 和 LOCATOR 的访问权限，仅允许 SYSTEM 和管理员组读取，阻止普通用户查询这两项。同时审查所有使用 Eastman Work Management 3.21 的系统，迁移至受支持的最新版本或替代产品，因为该版本以明文存储密码且厂商已停止安全支持。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=93034788412494&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/485","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2303"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1121.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0384","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0384.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0748","title":"Red Hat Linux net-tools 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Red Hat Linux 发行版中的 net-tools 软件包存在多处缓冲区溢出漏洞。该软件包包含 ifconfig、netstat 等常用网络配置与诊断工具，由于在解析网络接口名称、参数等输入时未对边界进行充分校验，导致缓冲区可被超长输入覆盖。本地或邻近网络的攻击者在调用相关工具时可构造超长参数或特制网络数据，触发溢出并可能覆写内存执行任意代码，从而提升权限或造成程序崩溃拒绝服务。该漏洞影响使用存在缺陷版本的 Red Hat net-tools 包的系统，攻击需具备本地执行相关工具或向受影响服务传递恶意输入的条件。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0748"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-06-24T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:58.483","remediation":"升级 net-tools 包至修复了缓冲区溢出漏洞的安全版本，Red Hat 用户可通过 RHSA1999:017 公告获取补丁并执行 yum update net-tools 完成升级。如暂时无法升级，应通过文件系统权限限制普通用户对 ifconfig、route、netstat 等网络管理命令的执行权限，仅允许 root 或授权管理员运行，以缩小攻击面。同时建议在防火墙层面限制不必要的网络扫描和外部探测，降低远程利用风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/RHSA1999017_01.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/184a5a0fb7dfcbb1c5bcfd5178078c78dc1e4738/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0748.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0748","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0748.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/95eeda559fd899397df50f658cf25cf01bb1e4ea/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0748.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8b1565557a8e0fb04634f0989d7e7dd7febd4847/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-hq84-7cq5-4g4j/GHSA-hq84-7cq5-4g4j.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0748.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x7000/6797/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0384.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0873","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0873.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1019","title":"Cabletron Spectrum Enterprise Manager 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Cabletron Spectrum Enterprise Manager 5.0 的 SpectroSERVER 组件在安装目录树时设置了不安全的文件权限，允许本地用户将特权可执行文件 processd 替换为木马程序。一旦成功替换，攻击者可利用该程序以 root 或 Administrator 权限执行任意代码，从而完全控制目标系统。该漏洞影响运行 Cabletron Spectrum Enterprise Manager 5.0 的服务器，攻击者需具备本地访问权限才能利用此漏洞。建议管理员立即检查并修正目录权限设置，防止未授权文件替换。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1019"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-06-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:32.087","remediation":"升级到 Cabletron Spectrum Enterprise Manager 已修复该问题的后续版本（5.0 补丁集或更高），并使用 chmod/chown 将 SpectroSERVER 安装目录及 processd 可执行文件权限收紧为仅 root/Administrator 可写（如 755 且属主为特权账户），移除其他用户的写权限；在无法立即升级时，通过文件系统 ACL 限制目录写入并定期校验 processd 完整性哈希作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93024398513475&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93024398713491&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/495","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/73dad9db65989a09e468a4f3a98f0eea36f0346c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1019.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1019","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1019.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/57cb981038a97031bd95a35a9b10bbed18ca4725/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1019.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/90b464bbc2d1b64270a5771429f96b67fbe9e79b/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3523-w4qj-m836/GHSA-3523-w4qj-m836.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1019.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000676.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--6cb591ae-8fdb-4e3e-a926-63891ce61612.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0873.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0500","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0500.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0723","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 CSRSS 工作线程耗尽拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 的客户端服务器运行时子系统（CSRSS）存在工作线程耗尽漏洞，当所有工作线程均处于等待用户输入状态时，系统无法处理新的请求，导致拒绝服务。远程攻击者可通过发送大量特定请求耗尽 CSRSS 工作线程池，使目标系统服务中断。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 系统，攻击者无需认证即可触发，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0723"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-06-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:55.320","remediation":"升级到 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 6a 或更高版本，该补丁通过限制 CSRSS 工作线程的并发请求数量来防止线程池耗尽。由于 Windows NT 4.0 已停止支持，建议升级到受支持的 Windows Server 版本（如 Windows Server 2019/2022）以获得持续安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ233323","http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-049.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/478","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-021","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0f25967d744704fe14324ac10f2b57e945aed081/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0723.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0723","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0723.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d2eb55660fa7a900eec90103b031be5d6f98d9ec/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0723.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1dbd44058e428445290bfb1f6fc6ecc0addbfd35/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3v56-gpqv-vh3w/GHSA-3v56-gpqv-vh3w.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0723.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000675.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--6a56c6de-e9f5-4fb6-b3d8-cee33c5464ac.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0500.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0331","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0331.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0731","title":"KDE klock 程序会话锁定绕过漏洞","description":"KDE 桌面环境的 klock 屏幕锁定程序存在输入验证缺陷，本地攻击者可通过向该程序提交特制格式错误的输入数据绕过屏幕锁定验证机制，无需输入正确密码即可解锁当前用户会话，获取未授权的系统访问权限。该漏洞影响 KDE 1.x 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。利用条件为攻击者需具备目标系统的本地访问权限。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0731"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-06-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:56.367","remediation":"升级至 KDE 1.1.2 及以上版本（1999年8月发布）即可修复该漏洞。该版本在 kscreensaver 的密码验证流程中增加了 timer.stop() 调用，消除了密码输入与对话框销毁之间的竞态条件，防止恶意格式输入绕过锁屏。如无法升级，作为临时缓解措施可禁用 klock 锁屏程序，改用第三方屏幕锁定工具替代。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/489","https://github.com/KDE/kde1-kdebase/commit/04906bd5de2f220bf100b605dad37b4a1d9a91a6","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f4ffb7bcd93209aa53a757a7ebdf17fe2a18eb33/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0731.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0731","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0731.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/bcb2bc8aed064ca80cf72b28e99ae813ae48a2c2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0731.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-j8vq-qmgj-pjpx/GHSA-j8vq-qmgj-pjpx.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/stats/explore_metadata.ipynb","https://github.com/Chaomeng-Lu/ICVul/blob/3dc55046764ea049e2a57d982699256e65909db9/scripts/cve_filtering.ipynb","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/woc-hack/kjd/blob/19869588676a19dd91ecd601bd03bb001278289b/output.demo1/out1/log.error"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0331.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0729","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0729.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0929","title":"Novell NetWare HTTP Server 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Novell NetWare 操作系统中集成的 Novell-HTTP-Server 及第三方 YAWN Web 服务器存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需认证即可通过向服务器发送大量 HTTP GET 请求，耗尽服务器连接池与处理资源，导致服务器无法响应合法用户请求，造成服务中断。该漏洞利用方式简单，攻击门槛极低，属于典型的资源耗尽型 DoS 攻击。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0929"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-16","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 Novell NetWare 至厂商修复版本或安装最新补丁。对于已停止维护的旧版本，建议在网络边界部署反向代理或 Web 应用防火墙（WAF），配置请求速率限制（rate limiting）和连接数阈值，限制单个 IP 的并发连接数及每秒请求数，以缓解大量 HTTP GET 请求导致的资源耗尽攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0929","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0929"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0729.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0729.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0729.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0520","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0520.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0730","title":"G. Wilford man 符号链接攻击本地文件覆盖漏洞","description":"Debian man-db 软件包中的 zsoelim 程序存在符号链接（symlink）攻击漏洞。zsoelim 在处理文件时未正确验证文件路径，本地攻击者可创建一个指向目标系统敏感文件的符号链接，当 zsoelim 跟随该符号链接处理文件时，将导致目标文件被覆盖，从而造成任意文件写入。攻击条件为本地低权限用户即可触发，无需远程访问。该漏洞影响 Debian man-db 2.3.10 等早期版本，CVSS v2 评分 10.0，危害等级为高危，可能导致权限提升或系统文件被破坏。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0730"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-06-12T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:56.240","remediation":"升级 man-db 软件包至当前稳定版本（2.9.x 或更高），该漏洞存在于 zsoelim 的符号链接处理逻辑中，新版已修复此问题。执行 apt update && apt upgrade man-db 完成更新。作为临时缓解措施，可移除 zsoelim 的 setuid/setgid 位（chmod u-s,g-s /usr/bin/zsoelim），并避免在受信目录以外使用 man 工具，同时在 /tmp 等临时目录挂载时启用 noexec 和限制符号链接创建。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0730","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19243","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0f25967d744704fe14324ac10f2b57e945aed081/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0730.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0730","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0730.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d2eb55660fa7a900eec90103b031be5d6f98d9ec/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0730.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1dbd44058e428445290bfb1f6fc6ecc0addbfd35/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9cm4-vwcc-jvg8/GHSA-9cm4-vwcc-jvg8.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0730.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/debiancn/debian.org/blob/6abc98daa6356b20e410013a6920b3764af682d4/english/security/1999/19990612.data","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict","https://github.com/VulnerabilityHistoryProject/mega-foss/blob/4829eeb7b0101570abbc87d2a697f2c0c2f4e5c3/src/cve/graphql/trial.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0520.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0520.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0520.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0307","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0307.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0713","title":"Compaq Tru64 UNIX dtlogin 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Compaq Tru64 UNIX 系统中的 dtlogin 程序存在权限提升漏洞。该程序在处理用户认证时未能正确验证权限，导致本地攻击者可通过向 dtlogin 发送特制请求或利用其不安全的文件权限，获取 root 权限。攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限，成功利用后可完全控制受影响系统。该漏洞影响 Compaq Tru64 UNIX 多个版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0713"],"sources":["cve","avd"],"published":"1999-06-11","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"Compaq Tru64 UNIX 已停止支持，建议迁移至受支持操作系统。如无法迁移，可移除 dtlogin 程序的 setuid root 权限位（chmod u-s /usr/dt/bin/dtlogin），并限制可登录控制台的用户组，仅允许受信任管理员使用本地控制台。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-044.shtml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0307.toml"}]